Also on a side note, a friend gave me a Brahmn's(sp?) Horn he got off a
named Mino in Beholder Maze. NPC merchant's offer over 3 plat for it. I

wind intrament. Anyone else have any experience with this item? I did try
the indentify song on it but no additional info.Rokenn Swiftsong
